import Vue from 'vue' //引入Vue对象
import Router from 'vue-router'//引入路由
//1:引入Exam01.vue 组件
import Exam01 from"./components/web1910/exam/Exam01.vue"
// 2:引入Exam02.vue组件
import Exam02 from "./components/web1910/exam/Exam02.vue"
import Exam03 from "./components/web1910/exam/Exam03.vue"
import Exam04 from "./components/web1910/exam/Exam04.vue"
import Fa06 from "./components/web1910/exam/Fa06.vue"
import Home from "./components/web1910/weixin/Home.vue"
import messageList from "./components/web1910/weixin/common/messageList.vue"
import login from "./components/web1910/xz/login.vue"
import product from "./components/web1910/xz/product.vue"
import cart from "./components/web1910/xz/cart.vue"
Vue.use(Router)
export default new Router({
  routes: [
    //配置组件
    {path:'/Exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/Exam02',component:Exam02},
    {path:'/Exam03',component:Exam03},
    {path:'/Exam04',component:Exam04},
    {path:"/Fa06",component:Fa06},
    {path:"/Home",component:Home},
    {path:"/messageList", component:messageList},
    {path:"/login",component:login},
    {path:"/product",component:product},
    {path:"/cart",component:cart}
  ]
})
